  "hinge": {
    "identity_□": "The Word is God-with-God, source of life and light; the Son makes the Father known; Jesus is identified as the Lamb and Son upon whom the Spirit remains.",
    "enactment_◇": "The Word comes into the world and becomes flesh, dwelling among us; John testifies; Jesus turns, asks, invites, calls, and names as people follow and come near.",
    "effect_Δ": "Darkness does not overcome the light; those who receive are given new birth; the first disciples stay, confess, and are promised an opened heaven centered on the Son of Man.",
